item.title: Could Somebody PLEASE add a ::staffzone teleport to my PI?
item.dc:creator: @_Java6 `Java
item.description:
@_Java6 wrote:

[quote=“Redemtion, post:6, topic:414776”][quote author=`Java link=topic=516736.msg3752094#msg3752094 date=1316123564]
Are you just trying to make the command to teleport you to a staff zone or are you trying to make an entire staff zone?

If just a teleport, add

[quote] if (playerCommand.equals(“staffzone”) && c.playerRights >= 2) {
c.getPA().movePlayer(x, y, 12);
}[/quote]

in with your other teleport commands in command.java, that’s for mod+

You really should know how to do that already though lol
[/quote]
isnt playerRights 2 admin? lul you might wanna try 1 because I’m pretty sure 2 is admin…[/quote]

Yeah, you’re right. Fixed.
